      "title": "Sanctuary Designation (Word of Recall)",
      "category": "religion",
      "content": "**Purpose**: This temple can be designated as a sanctuary for the **Word of Recall** spell.\n\n**Spell Reference**: *Word of Recall* (Level 6 Conjuration, Cleric)\n- **Casting Time**: Action\n- **Range**: 5 feet\n- **Components**: V\n- **Duration**: Instantaneous\n\n**Sanctuary Setup**: A cleric must cast *Word of Recall* in this temple to designate it as their sanctuary. Once designated, they can teleport themselves and up to 5 willing creatures here from anywhere.\n\n**Building Properties**:\n- **Dimensions**: 60ft Ã— 80ft (main hall)\n- **Material**: Stone\n- **AC**: 17 (stone walls)\n- **HP**: 500+ (large structure)\n- **Features**: Double entrance doors, raised altar platform (+1ft elevation)\n- **Capacity**: ~50 worshippers in main hall",
